high_descs: Go left and then right and turn to the right again to face the purple pillow on the white couch.
Pick the purple pillow up from the couch.
Turn around and cross the room and then go left and stand in front of the small table to the right of the white chair.
Turn the lamp on the table to the right of the white chair on.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a pillow and turn a lamp on.

high_descs: Turn left then head to the sofa
Pick up the pillow on the sofa
Turn right then head to the side table with lamp
anns.task_desc: Examine the pillow by the light

high_descs: Walk around the perimeter of the room to reach the white couch in the middle, facing the front of it.
Pick up the purple pillow from the white couch.
Turn left to walk around the table, hang a left at the fireplace to reach the small table in the corner with a chair next to it.
Turn on the lamp on the small table.
anns.task_desc: Look at a purple pillow under a lit lamp.
